OL,3,CCustomers in limbo as fire takes out
OL,4,CBrittany Ferries' booking system
OL,6,FSome customers and tour operators have
OL,7,Fbeen left unable to make bookings
OL,8,Fthrough Brittany Ferries' website and
OL,9,Fover the phone for nearly a week after
OL,10,Fa major data centre fire in the
OL,11,FNetherlands.
OL,13,FThe company's reservations system for
OL,14,Fits Guernsey operations has been down
OL,15,Fsince last Thursday - affecting routes
OL,16,Fto Poole, Portsmouth, St Malo and
OL,17,FJersey.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/9
