OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1779027072
OL,3,CCustomers in limbo as fire takes out
OL,4,CBrittany Ferries' booking system
OL,6,FDutch media report that a complex
OL,7,Fblaze at NorthC's site in Almere,
OL,8,Fclose to Amsterdam, led to a
OL,9,Fnationwide firefighting response and
OL,10,Fnetwork outages across the country,
OL,11,Fincluding at GP practices and Utrecht
OL,12,FUniversity.
OL,14,FThe centre, which is the size of
OL,15,Fnearly four football pitches, now has
OL,16,Fwhat NorthC describes as "temporary,
OL,17,Fredundant power and cooling", with
OL,18,Fsystems "being restarted in phases"
OL,19,Fand work to rejoin the main grid
OL,20,Funderway.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/9
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,390,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1779027072
OL,3,CCustomers in limbo as fire takes out
OL,4,CBrittany Ferries' booking system
OL,6,FMeanwhile, the impact on Brittany
OL,7,FFerries and those who rely on them has
OL,8,Fbeen significant.
OL,10,FGrant Miller, who lives in Surrey and
OL,11,Fowns the travel company Preston
OL,12,FHolidays, says the disruption has
OL,13,Falready likely cost them #20,000.
OL,15,FHe says: "We do 100% ferry-based
OL,16,Fholidays, so without the ferry we've
OL,17,Fgot no business.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/9
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,390,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1779027072
OL,3,CCustomers in limbo as fire takes out
OL,4,CBrittany Ferries' booking system
OL,6,F"We can't amend any bookings we
OL,7,Falready have, we can't place any
OL,8,Fprospective bookings that customers
OL,9,Fare willing to pay for, we're trying
OL,10,Fto get hotels to save availability in
OL,11,Fthe hope that ferries will be
OL,12,Favailable when it comes back on.
OL,14,FGrant says that before Brittany
OL,15,FFerries took over Condor, he used to
OL,16,Fbe able to send a fax or email to the
OL,17,Fcompany at the start of a new season
OL,18,Fand staff would manually book trips
OL,19,Fonce the system was live, but this is
OL,20,Fno longer an option.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/9
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,390,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1779027072
OL,3,CCustomers in limbo as fire takes out
OL,4,CBrittany Ferries' booking system
OL,6,FIf the situation is not resolved soon,
OL,7,Fhe adds: "We're going to have to
OL,8,Fpromote Jersey instead because the
OL,9,Fferries are running - try to steer
OL,10,Fpeople there to salvage bookings and
OL,11,Fstill make some money to keep the
OL,12,Fbusiness going.
OL,14,F"We had enough problems last year with
OL,15,Fthe disruption from the split of
OL,16,FJersey and Guernsey ferries; we were
OL,17,Fjust coming back and starting to grow
OL,18,Fthe business again post Covid and now
OL,19,Fwe've got this to contend with.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/9
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,390,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1779027072
OL,3,CCustomers in limbo as fire takes out
OL,4,CBrittany Ferries' booking system
OL,6,F"There are times with things like this
OL,7,Fwhere you think, 'How are we going to
OL,8,Fget visitors to the islands and is it
OL,9,Factually worth bothering?' because it
OL,10,Fdoes make it difficult.
OL,12,F"When you've got bookings you're
OL,13,Fhaving to turn away because people
OL,14,Fwant the certainty of going on holiday
OL,15,Fon X date and if they can't, they're
OL,16,Feither going to another operator who
OL,17,Fflies or another destination
OL,18,Faltogether.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G6/9
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,390,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1779027072
OL,3,CCustomers in limbo as fire takes out
OL,4,CBrittany Ferries' booking system
OL,6,F"If they're a regular customer to
OL,7,FGuernsey, they might decide they like
OL,8,Fwhere they've gone more and not come
OL,9,Fback."
OL,11,FIn response, Brittany Ferries has
OL,12,Fapologised and says: "We understand
OL,13,Fhow frustrating and disruptive the
OL,14,Fissues with our reservations system
OL,15,Fhave been for customers and are
OL,16,Fworking hard to restore normal service
OL,17,Fas quickly as possible.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G7/9
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,390,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38908
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1779027072
OL,3,CCustomers in limbo as fire takes out
OL,4,CBrittany Ferries' booking system
OL,6,F"In the meantime, passengers are still
OL,7,Fable to book travel either on the day
OL,8,Fbefore departure or on the day of
OL,9,Ftravel by visiting our port offices
OL,10,Facross the network.
OL,12,F"Customers can attend the Brittany
OL,13,FFerries' offices in St Peter Port,
OL,14,FPoole, Portsmouth and Saint Malo two
OL,15,Fhours prior to departure for travel as
OL,16,Feither foot passengers or with a
OL,17,Fvehicle.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G8/9
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,390,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38909
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1779027072
OL,3,CCustomers in limbo as fire takes out
OL,4,CBrittany Ferries' booking system
OL,6,F"Our third-party supplier Carus has
OL,7,Fassured us that the reservations
OL,8,Fsystem will be operational again by
OL,9,FThursday afternoon (14 May) and
OL,10,Fdiscussions are taking place to avoid
OL,11,Fsuch issues recurring in future."
OL,13,FAs Jersey goes to the polls and with
OL,14,FSenators back on the ballot, ITV
OL,15,FChannel's Jess Dunsdon and Luke
OL,16,FKeohane break down the key election
OL,17,Fissues alongside expert guests. Listen
OL,18,Fto Jersey Votes wherever you get your
OL,19,Fpodcasts or watch on ITVX, and YouTube
OL,20,Fbelow, with new episodes each
OL,21,FThursday...
